                        <li>Verify the conformity of operations in connection with their activities.</li>
                        <li>Intervene in specific assignments during changes in the legal organization of the Groupe.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="separator"></div>
            <div class="accounting page" id="accounting">
                <div class="ribbon accounting">
                    <span>A</span>
                </div>
                <span class="title">Accounting</span>
                <div class="article-paper">
                    <p>The Shared Services Centers offer services of general accounting, client accounts and supplier accounts, by country or by region.
                        They rely on common IT tools.</p>
                    <p>They contribute to the consolidation of human and technical competencies to:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Improve service quality</li>
                        <li>Secure handling of operations through standardized and documented processes</li>
                        <li>Strict application of Groupe procedures</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="separator"></div>
            <div class="procurement page" id="procurement">
                <div class="ribbon procurement">
                    <span>P</span>
                </div>
                <span class="title">Procurement</span>
                <div class="article-paper">
                    <p>The Shared Service Centers are the operational relays of implementation of
                        the Groupe's Purchasing policy. They allow agencies to focus on providing
                        the best day-to-day service to clients rather than spending time on negotiating and overseeing contracts.
                        For vendors, this system provides a single Groupe contact in each geographic zone and at a global level,
                        improving information exchange and enhancing their knowledge of the Groupe and our needs,
                        as well as simplifying the process to resolve any problems.</p>

                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="separator"></div>
            <div class="legal page" id="legal">
                <div class="ribbon legal">
                    <span>L</span>
                </div>
                <span class="title">Legal</span>
                <div class="article-paper">
                    <p>The Shared Service Centers can advise agencies about corporate law,
                        law of intellectual property, commercial law and social law.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="separator"></div>
            <div class="tax page" id="tax">
                <div class="ribbon tax">
                    <span>T</span>
                </div>
                <span class="title">Tax</span>
                <div class="article-paper">
                    <p>The Shared Services Centers provide tax return and advice service to internal clients(agencies) as below.</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Value added tax</li>
                        <li>Corporate tax</li>
                        <li>Individual income tax</li>
                        <li>Local tax</li>
                        <li>Property tax</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="separator"></div>
            <div class="hr page" id="hr">
                <div class="ribbon hr">
                    <span>H</span>
                </div>
                <span class="title">HR & Payroll</span>
                <div class="article-paper">
                    <p>The Shared Service Centers provide to agencies services related to administrative workforce management as:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Issuance of the pay slips </li>
                        <li>Preparation of social declarations </li>
                        <li>Management of social security coverage </li>
                        <li>Management of employment contracts </li>
                        <li>And assistance in relations with trade unions and representative bodiesï»¿ </li>
